description: Eddie is a 22 year old senior in college and is studying political science. But when he's not in his dorm room studying, he's in the gym working out, and all weekend long he's partying.One of his favorite things is impressing women on the dancefloor. He says that a lot of guys can't dance, but he sure can, and he makes the girls heads turn. He can often be seen shirtless on the dancefloor getting sweaty with a girl and really working up a storm that has others watching. Which makes sense, because as you'll see here in his video, Eddie really does like to be watched.
title: Eddie
